Source.Name: fish
Source.Summary: A full-blown user-friendly command line shell
Source.Description: Fish is a smart and user-friendly command line shell for macOS, Linux, and the rest of the family. Fish includes features like syntax highlighting, autosuggest-as-you-type, and fancy tab completions that just work, with no configuration required.
